record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 1665
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 1665 -- (House of Representatives - April 09, 2008)

[Page: H2099]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that my name be removed as a cosponsor of H.R. 1665.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Pennsylvania?
